oai_dc:dc.dc:description: I have been asked to share with you some of the ideas that we have used in our multiple man food animal practice over the past 23 years. We have had the good fortune to be invited to write a guest article in some of the different farm publications over the last years and the responsibility for these columns have fallen on several different people in that time span.
